We recommended Management to:
Instruct the Municipal Accountant and Municipal Treasurer to reconcile their records and make the corresponding adjustments. Likewise, the former must (1) reconcile and adjust the unexpended balance of 5% Calamity Fund and Cash in Bank-LDRRMF and (2) transfer the correct CIB-LDRRMF as back-up of TL-DRRMF in the Trust Fund books and the Municipal Treasurer must transfer its corresponding cash to the Trust Fund Regular account;
